{"tid":1540953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企要人！十點窗邊叫五大訴求，缺一不可！","createTime":"2019-09-04T13:01:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T14:47:52.000Z","uid":185628,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"14acf35474623ea5cd3c9f86226c15b54cca6d1a","tid":1540953,"uid":185628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:01:00.000Z","msg":"香港正值危急存亡之秋<br />\n要應對林鄭分化毒計<br />\n唯有宣示民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n十點窗邊叫五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n要有冇人叫就我叫先嘅精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我可以柒， 香港唔可以輸<br />\n請以三個方式支持呢個活動<br />\n1. 在地區facebook、telegram群組廣傳<br />\n2. 呼籲相熟嘅同路人<br />\n3. 自己領唱"},{"pid":"daf048ab5a7d11637960ccc170955c804dfea0b4","tid":1540953,"uid":93350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:01:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6704d5f03be39afd9989c6cdb3863662a57cccd","tid":1540953,"uid":185628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:08:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4580777ad70c0310364fbf65512ff103ce312db5","tid":1540953,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:11:12.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n跪求大家幫手推呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《急推》 前線唔好餓死呀<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1540938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1540938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5d4836a1560c7662d9a8a3f55ff188a79ee6934e","tid":1540953,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:11:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f9c61013b42a0d199bbbb8a25bb4884c22b31472","tid":1540953,"uid":185628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:13:18.000Z","msg":"和理非非多流汗， 前線義士少流血"},{"pid":"88be73909f735b65b96037ae446c2ae014ec3b3c","tid":1540953,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:18:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfac3178e6107ee6006ded36c884932178e595b6","tid":1540953,"uid":185628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:39:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b72610d4e49277dda32b37221622f69ca5dd1ad","tid":1540953,"uid":185628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:46:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e382651a6c04a4578a41464bc8297ff0533f0dcf","tid":1540953,"uid":306692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"